title: A Mano Gin & Burgers
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Western, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Offers a vegan burger and it can be used for whatever burger you choose. The buns are also vegan, as are papas bravas without the sauce. In addition has salads and grilled veggies (parrillada de verduras). Relocated from 4 Poniente 416 in 2015.
